name: Spiderman Shorts
description:
These shorts are a great way for your Spidey fan to sport a little super hero action. The pockets are done in red because that is my son's favorite color but they can be done in a shade of blue or even in the same Spiderman material as the rest of the shorts. These shorts are lightweight and still have real pockets that can be used to carry whatever it is that your super hero needs for the day.

This item is available in sizes 18m - size 12. Please indicate the size needed in the comments section at the time of purchase.

name: Buzz Lightyear Dress
description:
This dress features Buzz Lightyear from Disney's Toy Story. The two tone nature brings the character fabric out. Your little girl will love the way the skirt flares when she twirls in it. This dress is cotton and lightweight. It makes the perfect year round dress. In the fall and spring it can be paired with a long or short sleeve shirt (as you can see in some of the pictures). In the winter you can add tights or leggings to it and in the summer it can be worn as is.
